[31m-## [0.2.5] — 2026-05-11[m
[31m-[m
[31m-### Added[m
[31m-[m
[31m-- **Grounded Sentiment Analyst.** The renamed `sentiment_analyst` now reads[m
[31m-  real Yahoo News, StockTwits, and Reddit data before generating its report,[m
[31m-  replacing the prior flow that could fabricate social posts under prompt[m
[31m-  pressure. (#557, #607)[m
[31m-- **MiniMax provider** with the full M2.x catalog (M2.7 / M2.5 / M2.1 / M2[m
[31m-  plus highspeed variants, 204K context). Dual-region: Global[m
[31m-  (`MINIMAX_API_KEY`) and China (`MINIMAX_CN_API_KEY`).[m
[31m-- **Dual-region Qwen and GLM** with separate keys per region — international[m
[31m-  (`DASHSCOPE_API_KEY`, `ZHIPU_API_KEY`) and China (`DASHSCOPE_CN_API_KEY`,[m
[31m-  `ZHIPU_CN_API_KEY`), selectable via a secondary region prompt. (#758)[m
[31m-- **`AXONAI_*` env-var configurability for `DEFAULT_CONFIG`.** Override[m
[31m-  `llm_provider`, deep/quick model IDs, `backend_url`, `output_language`,[m
[31m-  debate-round counts, checkpoint flag, and benchmark ticker via `.env` with[m
[31m-  type-aware coercion (string / int / bool). (#602)[m
[31m-- **Interactive API-key detection in the CLI.** When the selected provider's[m
[31m-  key is missing, the CLI prompts for it and persists the value to `.env`[m
[31m-  so the analysis run continues without restart.[m
[31m-- **Remote Ollama support.** `OLLAMA_BASE_URL` points the CLI and the[m
[31m-  programmatic client at a remote `ollama-serve`. The CLI surfaces the[m
[31m-  resolved endpoint and warns on common malformed inputs. Adds a[m
[31m-  `"Custom model ID"` option for models pulled via `ollama pull`. (#648, #768)[m
[31m-- **Configurable news-fetch parameters** in `DEFAULT_CONFIG` — per-ticker[m
[31m-  article limit, macro headline limit, lookback window, and macro search[m
[31m-  queries. (#606, #683)[m
[31m-- **Configurable alpha benchmark** for non-US tickers. Replaces hardcoded[m
[31m-  SPY with regional indices for `.NS` (^NSEI), `.T` (^N225), `.HK` (^HSI),[m
[31m-  `.L` (^FTSE), `.TO` (^GSPTSE), `.AX` (^AXJO), `.BO` (^BSESN); explicit[m
[31m-  `benchmark_ticker` override available. Eliminates FX drift dominating[m
[31m-  alpha for non-USD listings. (#628, #684)[m
[31m-- **Multi-language output covers every user-facing agent** — researchers,[m
[31m-  risk debators, research manager, and trader, ending the previous[m
[31m-  partial-localization reports. (#575)[m
[31m-- **Model catalog refresh.** OpenAI GPT-5.5 frontier, Anthropic Claude Opus[m
[31m-  4.7, Gemini 3.1 Flash-Lite GA, xAI Grok 4.20, Qwen 3.6 line. Versioned IDs[m
[31m-  only; auto-shifting aliases moved to the `"Custom model ID"` option.[m
[31m-[m
[31m-### Changed[m
[31m-[m
[31m-- **Sentiment Analyst** is now consistently named across the CLI dropdown,[m
[31m-  status panel, and final reports (previously the backend was renamed but[m
[31m-  the CLI still said "Social Analyst"). The `AnalystType.SOCIAL = "social"`[m
[31m-  wire value is kept for saved-config back-compat.[m
[31m-[m
[31m-### Fixed[m
[31m-[m
[31m-- **Structured output works on DeepSeek V4 / reasoner and MiniMax M2.x.**[m
[31m-  Those providers reject `tool_choice` per their tool-calling docs; the[m
[31m-  binding flow now skips it automatically via a capability table.[m
[31m-- **`pip install .` installations pick up the project `.env`** when running[m
[31m-  the CLI as a console script. (#747)[m
[31m-- **Reports save end-to-end** — streamed chunks were previously dropped from[m
[31m-  `complete_report.md`. (#719, #736)[m
[31m-- **Ticker prompt preserves exchange suffixes** (`.SH`, `.SZ`, `.SS`, `.HK`,[m
[31m-  `.T`, etc.) for A-share, HK, Tokyo, and other non-US flows. (#770)[m
[31m-- **Docker permission errors** no longer block first-run write to[m
[31m-  `~/.axonai/`. (#519, #627, #672, #771)[m
[31m-- **Config state no longer leaks between runs** when sub-dicts are mutated;[m
[31m-  `set_config` partial updates preserve sibling defaults. (#788)[m
[31m-- **`max_recur_limit` config actually applies** — previously read but not[m
[31m-  forwarded to the propagator. (#764)[m
[31m-- **Missing-API-key error** names the exact env var to set. (#680)[m
[31m-- **Quieter startup** — suppressed the noisy upstream[m
[31m-  `LangChainPendingDeprecationWarning` from langgraph-checkpoint; will be[m
[31m-  removed once that package ships its fix.[m
[31m-[m
[31m-### Security[m
[31m-[m
[31m-- **Ticker path-traversal validation** at every filesystem-path site (cache,[m
[31m-  checkpoint database, results) so a malicious ticker cannot escape its[m
[31m-  intended directory. (#618)[m
