[31m-## 🏗️ Architecture Overview[m
[31m-[m
[31m-The system operates as a continuous real-time loop divided into three specialized layers, keeping API token costs low by using pure math for event filtering:[m
[31m-[m
[31m-```[m
[31m-┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐[m
[31m-│  LAYER 3 — LLM GRAPH (fires only on high-priority events)  │[m
[31m-│  AxonAIGraph → Trader → [Analysts x4] → Bull/Bear →        │[m
[31m-│  ResearchMgr → [Risk x3] → PortfolioManager → Decision     │[m
[31m-│  (Triggered on cooldown, e.g. 300s, when priority >= MED)   │[m
[31m-├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤[m
[31m-│  LAYER 2 — DETECTION ENGINE (pure math, zero tokens)       │[m
[31m-│  EventDetector: 9 structural indicators & pattern checks   │[m
[31m-│  LiveWorldState: spread / session / ATR / RSI / regime      │[m
[31m-│  LiveMarketEvidence: swing H/L / key levels / patterns      │[m
[31m-├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤[m
[31m-│  LAYER 1 — TICK ENGINE (100ms MT5 poll loop)               │[m
[31m-│  TickEngine → CandleBuilder (M1/M5/M15/H1) → callbacks     │[m
[31m-│  MT5 raw ticks → OHLCV → candle close events               │[m
[31m-└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘[m
[31m-          ↕ WebSocket ↕[m
[31m-┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐[m
[31m-│  DASHBOARD (FastAPI + HTML5 CSS Glassmorphism HUD)         │[m
[31m-│  /ws — live streams ticks, indicators, events & agent state │[m
[31m-└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘[m
[31m-```[m
[31m-[m
[31m-### Signal Flow:[m
[31m-`MT5 Tick` ➔ `TickEngine` ➔ `CandleBuilder` ➔ `EventDetector` ➔ `queue.Queue` ➔ `AxonDaemon` ➔ `GraphExecutor` ➔ `LangGraph` ➔ `PM Decision` ➔ `Dashboard`[m
[31m-[m
